<h2>Colour spread</h2>
Apply a range to each colour channel (+/-). The range defines the background for autocropping.
<hr>
<h3>Example</h3>
<br>
<br>
<strong>Background colour:</strong> 250,250,250
<br>
<br>
By setting the colour spread to 5, the background is defined as 245,245,245 - 255,255,255 for the purpose of autocropping.

